·Phototrexate<ref name="MateraGomila2018">{{cite journal|last1=Matera|first1=Carlo|last2=Gomila|first2=Alexandre M. J.|last3=Camarero|first3=Núria|last4=Libergoli|first4=Michela|last5=Soler|first5=Concepció|last6=Gorostiza|first6=Pau|title=Photoswitchable Antimetabolite for Targeted Photoactivated Chemotherapy|journal=Journal of the American Chemical Society|volume=140|issue=46|year=2018|pages=15764–15773|issn=0002-7863|doi=10.1021/jacs.8b08249|pmid=30346152|hdl=2445/126377}}</ref>

抗代謝物會偽裝成[[嘌呤|嘌呤]]（硫唑嘌呤，巰基嘌呤）或[[嘧啶|嘧啶]]等化學物質(這些化學物質原本是構成DNA的物質)。而抗代謝物可以防止嘌呤、嘧啶等在[[細胞週期|細胞週期]]的S期中進入DNA，進而可以阻止正常發育和細胞分裂。<ref>Takimoto CH, Calvo E. [https://www.cancernetwork.com/articles/principles-oncologic-pharmacotherapy "Principles of Oncologic Pharmacotherapy"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.cancernetwork.com/articles/principles-oncologic-pharmacotherapy |date=20200503080338 }} in Pazdur R, Wagman LD, Camphausen KA, Hoskins WJ (Eds) [http://www.cancernetwork.com/cancer-management-11/ Cancer Management: A Multidisciplinary Approach] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cancernetwork.com/cancer-management-11/ |date=20131004224102 }}. 11 ed. 2008.</ref>
由於抗代謝物可以參與生物合成過程中酶的結合點位的競爭以及將生物分子摻入核酸，從而抑制正常腫瘤細胞的功能並凋亡，因此這些藥物是使用上最廣泛的細胞制劑。也因為抗代謝物具有很高的細胞週期特異性，也可以[[標靶治療|標靶治療]]癌細胞的DNA複製<ref name="Antimetabolites">{{cite book|title=Medicinal Chemistry of Anticancer Drugs|edition=2nd|author=Avendano, Carmen|author2=Menendez Carlos J.|last-author-amp=yes|publisher=Elsevier Science|year=2015}}</ref>

